setApproved_(String) - Method in interface de.sfgmbh.applayer.core.definitions.IntfRoomAllocation
Set the approval status of the room allocation Valid status strings are:

"accepted" - The room allocation is approved by the organization
"denied" - The room allocation is denied by the organization
"waiting" - The room allocation is not yet reviewed by the organization
"counter" - The room allocation marks a counter proposal by the organization,
this should be changed to "accepted" or "denied" automatically as soon as
the lecturer accepts or denies the proposal.

setNewException(String, String, String) - Method in class de.sfgmbh.applayer.core.model.AppException
Set a new exception message, title and variant and update all observer

Valid status strings for the variant are:
"success" - The look and feel gets customized to indicate success
"info" - The look and feel gets customized for displaying information
"warn" - The look and feel gets customized for displaying warnings
"error" - The look and feel gets customized to show a problem

"error" is the default look and feel if no or an invalid variant was submitted.
